GETTING STARTED
==-==-==-==-==-==

-> show dbs {
    => Shows the list of data bases
}

-> use dbname {
    => Start using/connect to the db with the name "dbname"
    => If the db with the name "dbname" not present then it is automatically created
}

-> db.collectionName.insertOne({json}) {
    => If there is no collection with the name collectionName in the chosen DB (one we are presently connected to), it
       would be created and the insertOne would add the json to it
}

-> db.collectionName.find().pretty() {
    => This command till find() prints the records of the collection
    => Use of the pretty() shows the data in the formatted JSON structure
}